relation: One of the PigTower things from EB64. I so wish that they'd have made it to M3.

I painted this for Stevesesy as a way of saying "thanks" for lending me Mother 3. In case you don't recognize it: http://starmen.net/vote/vote.php?id=1763 Yeah, it's silly, but I had fun making it anyway. I thought it was a hoot.
A painting of Mr. Saturn I did on a CD wallet thing for Stevesesy. I scanned it before I sent that and Mother 3 back to him, which he was so EXCEEDINGLY kind to lend me.
Had done this a while back for a project. But since I won't be using this graphic anymore, here it is.
